rules.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT id, category, status, numeric_col, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY numeric_col), RANK() OVER (ORDER BY numeric_col), DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY numeric_col), NTILE(1000) OVER (ORDER BY numeric_col), LAG(numeric_col, 1) OVER (ORDER BY id), LAG(numeric_col, 2) OVER (ORDER BY id), LAG(numeric_col, 3) OVER (ORDER BY id), LAG(numeric_col, 4) OVER (ORDER BY id), LAG(numeric_col, 5) OVER (ORDER BY id), LAG(numeric_col, 6) OVER (ORDER BY id), LAG(numeric_col, 7) OVER (ORDER BY id), LAG(numeric_col, 8) OVER (ORDER BY id), LAG(numeric_col, 9) OVER (ORDER BY id), LAG(numeric_col, 10) OVER (ORDER BY id), LEAD(numeric_col, 1) OVER (ORDER BY id), LEAD(numeric_col, 2) OVER (ORDER BY id), LEAD(numeric_col, 3) OVER (ORDER BY id), LEAD(numeric_col, 4) OVER (ORDER BY id), LEAD(numeric_col, 5) OVER (ORDER BY id), LEAD(numeric_col, 6) OVER (ORDER BY id), LEAD(numeric_col, 7) OVER (ORDER BY id), LEAD(numeric_col, 8) OVER (ORDER BY id), LEAD(numeric_col, 9) OVER (ORDER BY id), LEAD(numeric_col, 10) OVER (ORDER BY id), SUM(numeric_col) OVER (ORDER BY id ROWS BETWEEN 1000 PRECEDING AND 1000 FOLLOWING), AVG(numeric_col) OVER (ORDER BY id ROWS BETWEEN 500 PRECEDING AND 500 FOLLOWING), MIN(numeric_col) OVER (ORDER BY id ROWS BETWEEN 250 PRECEDING AND 250 FOLLOWING), MAX(numeric_col) OVER (ORDER BY id ROWS BETWEEN 250 PRECEDING AND 250 FOLLOWING), STDDEV(numeric_col) OVER (ORDER BY id ROWS BETWEEN 100 PRECEDING AND 100 FOLLOWING), VARIANCE(numeric_col) OVER (ORDER BY id ROWS BETWEEN 100 PRECEDING AND 100 FOLLOWING) FROM stress_test_data WHERE id <= 800000)

rules.sql: SELECT category, SUM(POWER(numeric_col, 7)), SUM(EXP(numeric_col/100000000)), SUM(LOG(GREATEST(numeric_col, 1)) * LOG(GREATEST(numeric_col, 1)) * LOG(GREATEST(numeric_col, 1)) * LOG(GREATEST(numeric_col, 1)) * LOG(GREATEST(numeric_col, 1))), SUM(SQRT(SQRT(SQRT(SQRT(SQRT(ABS(numeric_col))))))), SUM(SIN(numeric_col/5000000) * COS(numeric_col/5000000) * TAN(numeric_col/5000000) * SIN(numeric_col/6000000) * COS(numeric_col/6000000)), SUM(TAN(numeric_col/500000000) * TAN(numeric_col/500000000) * TAN(numeric_col/500000000) * TAN(numeric_col/500000000) * TAN(numeric_col/500000000)), AVG(POWER(numeric_col, 6) + SQRT(ABS(numeric_col)) + LOG(GREATEST(numeric_col, 1)) + EXP(numeric_col/200000000) + SIN(numeric_col/1000000)), STDDEV(LOG(GREATEST(numeric_col, 1)) * SQRT(ABS(numeric_col)) * SIN(numeric_col/2000000) * COS(numeric_col/2000000)) FROM stress_test_data WHERE id <= 1700000 GROUP BY category ORDER BY SUM(POWER(numeric_col, 7)) DESC

SELECT category, COUNT(*) FROM stress_test_data WHERE REGEXP_LIKE(text_col, '^Text_Value_[0-9]{1,7}$') AND REGEXP_LIKE(REVERSE(text_col), '^[0-9]{1,7}_eulaV_txeT$') AND LENGTH(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(text_col, 'T', ''), 'e', ''), 'x', ''), 't', ''), '_', ''), 'V', ''), 'a', ''), 'l', ''), 'u', ''), 'e', ''), '0', ''), '1', ''), '2', ''), '3', '')) >= 0 AND CONTAINS(UPPER(LOWER(UPPER(LOWER(UPPER(LOWER(UPPER(text_col))))))), 'VALUE') AND SUBSTRING(text_col, 1, 20) LIKE 'Text_Value_%' AND REVERSE(SUBSTRING(REVERSE(text_col), 1, 10)) LIKE '%[0-9]%' AND id <= 1400000 GROUP BY category HAVING COUNT(*) > 500

rules.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM stress_test_data a JOIN stress_test_data b ON a.category = b.category AND ABS(a.numeric_col - b.numeric_col) < 10000 JOIN stress_test_data c ON b.status = c.status AND ABS(b.numeric_col - c.numeric_col) < 8000 JOIN stress_test_data d ON c.category = d.category AND ABS(c.numeric_col - d.numeric_col) < 6000 WHERE a.id <= 30000 AND b.id <= 30000 AND c.id <= 30000 AND d.id <= 30000 AND a.priority = b.priority AND b.priority = c.priority AND c.priority = d.priority

rules.sql: SELECT category, status, priority, EXTRACT(YEAR FROM date_col), EXTRACT(MONTH FROM date_col), COUNT(*), SUM(numeric_col), AVG(numeric_col), MIN(numeric_col), MAX(numeric_col), STDDEV(numeric_col), VARIANCE(numeric_col), SUM(DISTINCT numeric_col), COUNT(DISTINCT numeric_col), MEDIAN(numeric_col), MODE(numeric_col), PERCENTILE_CONT(0.05) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY numeric_col), PERCENTILE_CONT(0.15) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY numeric_col), PERCENTILE_CONT(0.25) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY numeric_col), PERCENTILE_CONT(0.35) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY numeric_col), PERCENTILE_CONT(0.45) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY numeric_col), PERCENTILE_CONT(0.55) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY numeric_col), PERCENTILE_CONT(0.65) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY numeric_col), PERCENTILE_CONT(0.75) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY numeric_col), PERCENTILE_CONT(0.85) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY numeric_col), PERCENTILE_CONT(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY numeric_col) FROM stress_test_data WHERE id <= 1800000 GROUP BY category, status, priority, EXTRACT(YEAR FROM date_col), EXTRACT(MONTH FROM date_col) HAVING COUNT(*) > 100 ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM stress_test_data WHERE LENGTH(text_col) BETWEEN 12 AND 60 AND REGEXP_COUNT(text_col, '[0-9]') BETWEEN 2 AND 15 AND REGEXP_COUNT(text_col, '[A-Z]') BETWEEN 2 AND 25 AND REGEXP_COUNT(text_col, '[a-z]') BETWEEN 2 AND 25 AND REGEXP_COUNT(text_col, '_') = 2 AND SOUNDEX(text_col) IN (SELECT SOUNDEX('Value_' || seq4() || '_Text') FROM table(generator(rowcount => 2000))) AND EDIT_DISTANCE(text_col, 'Text_Value_Sample_Advanced_Test') < 20 AND REVERSE(UPPER(LOWER(REVERSE(UPPER(LOWER(text_col)))))) LIKE '%EULAV%' AND REPLACE(REPLACE(text_col, 'Text', 'XXXX'), 'Value', 'YYYY') LIKE 'XXXX_YYYY_%' AND id <= 1500000

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT a.id, a.category, b.status, c.priority, a.numeric_col + b.numeric_col + c.numeric_col as total_col FROM stress_test_data a, stress_test_data b, stress_test_data c WHERE a.id <= 2200 AND b.id <= 2200 AND c.id <= 2200 AND a.numeric_col > 100000 AND b.numeric_col > 100000 AND c.numeric_col > 100000 AND POWER(a.numeric_col, 2) + POWER(b.numeric_col, 2) + POWER(c.numeric_col, 2) > 500000000000 AND SIN(a.numeric_col/1000000) * COS(b.numeric_col/1000000) * TAN(c.numeric_col/1000000) > -1)
